data.text: @atetheSandwich As a die hard fan I wanted to love it....I didn’t hate it, but I found some parts very frustrating. Rory and her wild ways. Lorelai leaving Luke and going ‘Wild’. BUT I really grew to love Emily and I liked the wedding which was magical - Reflecting Light 😍😍
@elsbells78 I haven't heard of it! I'll check it out!
@elsbells78 Blegh, I did not like year in the life at allllllllll
@atetheSandwich Yesterday I binge watched the whole first season of Alexa & Katie on Netflix. It’s got Tiffani Thiessen from Saved By the Bell in it, playing Alexa’s mum. Have you seen it?
@atetheSandwich Buon Voyage ☔️ Always makes me cry at how much everyone loves Rory. Watch A Year in the Life to offset the pain of it being over...
